originalText.text:
Awesome company! I called them for a summer bash at my home and I was extremely satisfied.

Lance and his team were very informative leading up to the event. They were early to set up and we’re up and running FAST!

The unit itself was very clean and well kept. We had about 150 guests and everyone was very pleased.

When the event was over they left without issue. The team cleaned up after themselves and leafy my driveway just like they found it.

Best part of this was no clean up, no mess & no wear and tear on my home.

I highly recommend this vendor for a clean, quick and seamless service.
